{"tid":219393,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知係有登革熱定乜[sosad]","createTime":"2017-04-27T07:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T13:05:59.000Z","uid":52068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"071606a45edc228d7b3c487db93627ba6c33b614","tid":219393,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"話說就咁，小弟係大概7日之前比蚊針，印已消<br />\n<br />\n尋日起床發覺有D頭暈，個感覺有D似個腦同頭殼分開左咁，我老豆臨出門仲起勢咁朗我個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔會話太辛苦，就係有D唔係咁精神，9秒9衝去請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到夜晚有D肚痛，屙左幾次稀屎，但冇到水既程度<br />\n<br />\n今日起床又肚痛，又屙左幾次，屙完凍撚到仆街，攞左件羽絨出黎訓係梳發1個鐘都係凍到仆街，起身量下體溫哇屌！唔量就由自可，一量就嚇到屎都瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n39度幾，逼近40大關，再量多次，molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  升到我出世以黎既高位40.8<br />\n我上網揾資料<br />\n<br />\n登革熱：潛伏期通常為 4 &ndash; 7 天<br />\n              病徵包括突發的高燒、嚴重頭痛、眼窩後疼痛、肌肉及關節痛、食慾<br />\n               不振、嘔心及出疹。<br />\n              高溫可持續 2 &ndash; 7 天，而體溫甚至高達攝氏 40 &ndash; 41 度<br />\n              最嚴重的情況會導致血液循環系統衰竭、休克及死亡。<br />\n再睇埋日本腦炎，大鑊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又中幾個,屌你六合彩三獎又唔見我中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開始諗起我屋企人，然後突然發現自己連第一次都未試過，啊爸啊媽，我唔想死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇到台灣個衛生處話依D病最好2-3日先去驗，會準D。<br />\n<br />\n我依家39度幾，自閉係屋企，聽日仲係發燒先去睇急症<br />\n<br />\n希望我係自己嚇自己，聽日仲有機會上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後奉勸各位巴打，真係要留意環境衛生，特別係有種花個D清下積水<br />\n<br />\n祝  身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfaef7d0e51f1d6bf7e0f65c636585756048dca","tid":219393,"uid":17311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:51:21.000Z","msg":"依家即刻去睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a559cbce912485d384a0348859aecc09f5bb9f8a","tid":219393,"uid":25237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"依家仲唔去係咪想等到下世先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f59cbdd3ba52be72255e0f8cfe053a94a167c67","tid":219393,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"去左診所，攞左退燒藥，佢話其實可以睇下聽日情況點樣先決定"},{"pid":"a3b920d874b42c43c8b9152d5bfec9dc5c89158a","tid":219393,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:00:22.000Z","msg":"依家訓陣，6點起床"},{"pid":"671464174633d720059453288385739c0df66f8d","tid":219393,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:13:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b866092f9d63e2c8494737722b0c55439692d0a0","tid":219393,"uid":61853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"a85b55dd48cedbbf43faf6ea1f915745a7d2c2f8","tid":219393,"uid":53207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"我試過俾蚊咬到十幾下<br />\n之後有日忽然發高燒，頭痛，作嘔，攰到行唔到<br />\n點知第二日又乜事都冇<br />\n我懷疑係初次登革熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}